<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>City Of Ember</span>, <span>The Diamond Of Darkhold</span>, <span>The City Of Ember</span>, <span>The People Of Sparks</span>, <span>The Prophet Of Yonwood</span> </h3>
